doc.after: Swiss International Air Lines has its operational headquarters at EuroAirport Basel-Mulhouse-Freiburg[21][22] near Basel, Switzerland.[9] This French-Swiss binational airport is located on French territory and has customs-free access to Switzerland.[23] The Swiss head office is located in the Swiss section of the airport, and it is only accessible from Switzerland.[24] According to the commercial register, the legal seat is in Basel itself.[25]
